{"tid":1748574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又有偽黃鋪想食人血饅頭 入黎屌爆佢","createTime":"2019-11-23T17:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T17:38:48.000Z","uid":4819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0563b55500460179ae9eb01c8d63a2a2e35e8c04","tid":1748574,"uid":4819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T17:38:48.000Z","msg":"岩岩係facebook見到呢間野個廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌講撚到自己幾黃幾支持<br />\n講到無左幾多生意咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好有食人血饅頭嫌疑囉 仲要搵極都搵唔到佢講果套裝係邊 <br />\n之前果幾個月一直扮無野咁出緊啲團購post<br />\n而家博人去懲罰佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇番佢仲要勁核突咁加左香港加油個logo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係個logo 係11月22號先開始加<br />\n大佬呀 唔好咁肉酸啦 <br />\n有無手足一齊report 佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推爆呢啲人血饅頭鋪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zC6nPt6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzC6nPt6.png&h=be7348cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GAN6wHs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGAN6wHs.png&h=26c1e5e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ufbnPt8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FufbnPt8.png&h=6c41779d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}